quran[8{c,v,t}:
12,104,halaank tum is khidmat par un se koi ujrat bhi nahi mangte ho yeh to aik nasiyaat hai jo duniya walon ke liye aam hai
12,105,zameen aur asmano mein kitni hi nishanain hain jin par se yeh log guzarte rehtay hain aur zara tavajja nahi karte
12,106,un mein se aksar Allah ko mantay hain magar is terhan ke uss ke sath dosaron ko shareektehratay hain
12,107,kya yeh mutmaen hain ke khuda ke azaab ki koi bulaa inhen daboch nah le gi ya be khaberi mein qayamat ki gharri achanak un par nah aa jaye gi ?
12,108,"tum un se saaf keh do ke"" mera rasta to yeh hai, mein Allah ki taraf bulaataa hon, mein khud bhi poori roshni mein apna rasta dekh raha hon aur mere saathi bhi, aur Allah pak hai aur shirk karne walon se mera koi vaastaa nahi """
12,109,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay hum ne jo paighambar beje thay woh sab bhi ensaan hi thay, aur unhi bustiyon ke rehne walon mein se thay, aur aُnhi ki taraf hum wahi bhaijtay rahay hain phir kya yeh log zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke unn qomon ka injaam inhen nazar nah aaya jo un se pehlay guzar chuki hain? yaqeenan akhirat ka ghar unn logon ke liye aur ziyada behtar hai jinhon ne ( payghambaroon ki baat maan kar ) taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar ki kya ab bhi tum log nah samjhoo ge ?"
12,110,"( pehlay payghambaroon ke sath bhi yahi hota raha hai ke woh muddaton nasiyaat karte rahay aur logon ne sun kar nah diya ) yahan taq ke jab paighambar logon se mayoos ho gay aur logon ne bhi samajh liya ke unn se jhoot bola gaya tha, to yaka yak hamari madad payghambaroon ko poanch gayi phir jab aisa mauqa aa jata hai to hamara qaida yeh hai ke jisay hum chahtay hain bacha letay hain aur mujrimon par se to hamara azaab taalla hi nahi ja sakta"
12,111,aglay logon ke un qisson mein aqal o hosh rakhnay walon ke liye Ibrat hai yeh jo kuch quran mein bayan kya ja raha hai yeh banawati baatein nahi hain balkay jo kitaaben is se pehlay aayi hui hain unhi ki tasdeeq hai aur har cheez ki tafseel aur imaan laane walon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat
